OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fwith some hazy evening sunshine. It
OL,7,Fwill stay mostly dry overnight, but
OL,8,Fturning cloudy over northern Argyll
OL,9,Fand the Isles with the odd spot of
OL,10,Frain possible.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FIt will be dry throughout the
OL,13,Fday with variable cloud and some warm
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Generally cloudier over
OL,15,Fnorthern Argyll and the Isles.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
